    a: "Pay more for a Makita if you drill more than about 10 times a year. Makita's DHP484Z reaches 65 Nm against Ozito's 40 Nm. Its LXT battery platform also extends to a wide range of other tools. Ozito's 40 Nm and lower price cover most home tasks well enough for a handful of jobs a year.",
  },
