    q: 'Are Aldi or Lidl special-buy cordless drills any good?',
    a: "Aldi's Ferrex and Lidl's Parkside cordless drills are genuinely fine for a single one-off job if you catch the seasonal stock window. Neither is sold on Amazon UK. Their batteries only fit their own supermarket range. Treat either as a one-time task rather than an ongoing tool platform.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Is Titan a Toolstation brand or a Screwfix brand?',
    a: "Titan and Erbauer are both Screwfix own-brands. Toolstation carries no house power tool brand of its own. It resells trade brands including DeWalt, Milwaukee, Makita and Bosch instead.",
