  {
    q: 'Do own-brand cordless drills carry the same warranty as Makita or DeWalt?',
    a: "No. Titan and Mac Allister ship a flat 2 year guarantee with no registration step. Makita, DeWalt and Bosch default to a 1 year warranty and only extend to 3 years if you register the tool online within 30 days of purchase.",
