  {
    q: 'Can I use an own-brand battery in a premium drill?',
    a: "No. Erbauer EXT, Titan TXP, Mac Allister 18V and Ozito PXC batteries only fit their own tool range. Makita LXT, DeWalt XR, Bosch Professional 18V and Milwaukee M18 batteries are each locked to their own platform too. None of the ranges compared here cross-fit another brand's tools.",
